@startuml
title UC-3 E1 Door Panel LED 표시 실패

actor Driver
actor "Cluster / HMI System" as HMI
control "ChildLockController" as CLC
entity "ChildLockState" as CLS
boundary "Door Panel Interface" as DPI
database "Diagnostic Log" as LOG

CLC -> CLS : getState()
activate CLS
CLS --> CLC : childLockState
deactivate CLS

alt 차일드락 ON 상태
    CLC -> DPI : turnOnLED()
    activate DPI
else 차일드락 OFF 상태
    CLC -> DPI : turnOffLED()
    activate DPI
end

alt 표시 실패 응답 수신
    DPI --> CLC : displayFailed
else 응답 없음
    CLC -> CLC : timeoutDetected()
end

deactivate DPI

ref over CLC, HMI
  UC-4 시스템 개입 상황 알림 제공
  - Door Panel 표시 오류
  - 현재 차일드락 상태 표시
  - 운전자 확인 요청
end ref

CLC -> LOG : writeDisplayFailureLog()
@enduml
